        <center>
            <h2>
                <b>Administration of W. Storer How, June 1865-August 1865</b>
            </h2>
        </center>
        <br/>

        <hr width="80%"/>
        <center>
            <table border="0" width="76%">
                <tr>
                    <td>June 1865-August 1865 | <a href="bureau_how2.html">September 1865-November
                            1865</a> | <a href="bureau_how3.html">December 1865-February 1866</a> |
